{"tid":1825242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球10大「顏值乳值最高空姐航空公司」排名，第一名「光看到制服」讓大家都狂噴血啊....!","createTime":"2020-01-15T06:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T08:47:11.000Z","uid":297241,"like":7,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"295d5f004cec0a0265f1dc206e44b4b9be407d96","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"全球10大空姐最美的航空公司，她們可愛優雅還非常性感！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在越來越多人喜歡搭飛機出國去玩， 不管選哪家航空公司， 最令人印象深刻的一定是空姐啦。 而且每個航空公司的空姐， 特色又不太一樣， 究竟全球哪些航空公司的空姐最美呢？"},{"pid":"ce29b5306a0999eee450f10513b0a10edc0b23ea","tid":1825242,"uid":15605,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:07:38.000Z","msg":"圖呢屌你"},{"pid":"7f44ff0d55e2e60ef1fef69d1c89428cb11980e0","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"10、Virgin Atlantic 英國維珍大西洋航空<br />\n<br />\n維珍大西洋航空的空姐一向以引人注目的絲質領結和合身的紅色制服著稱。當他們服務乘客的時候所散發出來的品味，魅力和愉悅的精神，誰人能超越這些「紅色的性感寶貝」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=1kn0svv/1o7r000309n051onq3rp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1kn0svv%2F1o7r000309n051onq3rp.jpg&h=4364ddaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e065cadf292118c16f48cf4d359216b987d96c6","tid":1825242,"uid":60202,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:07:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://life.tw/?app=view&amp;no=667389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flife.tw%2F%3Fapp%3Dview%26no%3D667389&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=708605dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://life.tw/?app=view&amp;no=667389</a>"},{"pid":"7804f5275b80ca51db545da8164fd7369e82342f","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"9、Thai Airways International 泰國國際航空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰國航空是泰國國有航空公司，他們給每一次航班的乘客提供無微不至的服務。每一位空姐穿上美麗的紫色制服，給世人一個難以磨滅的印象。"},{"pid":"a3bf61a4f1ee6023406732df