islike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"9、Thai Airways International 泰國國際航空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰國航空是泰國國有航空公司，他們給每一次航班的乘客提供無微不至的服務。每一位空姐穿上美麗的紫色制服，給世人一個難以磨滅的印象。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://store.zhentoo.com/uploads/C/0B/C0B9F9CBBC.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.zhentoo.com%2Fuploads%2FC%2F0B%2FC0B9F9CBBC.jpeg&h=5694f43c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18543ce99d08c82eec7a0dab6bfceb22b153d9b6","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"68cdd4b21b7ce4de363e2de26ba528bf0f03b511","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84f17a282b716661fcb1b93c6b7f43177028336a","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:09:42.000Z","msg":"8、Lufthansa 德國漢莎航空<br />\n<br />\n漢莎航空與其空乘人員入選其中，背後自有它傲人的道理。她們的服務態度和彬彬有禮的舉止令其成為人們樂於乘坐的航班。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=vendec/1o7800060s334s7on4r9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dvendec%2F1o7800060s334s7on4r9.jpg&h=5ba24c64&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://store.zhentoo.com/uploads/7/F0/7F09F97086.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.zhentoo.com%2Fuploads%2F7%2FF0%2F7F09F97086.jpeg&h=08b2fac1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07fedd38f931bcc7daea0110d50770ab8d0470c4","tid":1825242,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:14:51.000Z","msg":"張張矇矇地"},{"pid":"2e94a121d47dad14c74a66ae3be19935a6dbb602","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:15:10.000Z","msg":"7、Air Asia 亞洲航空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亞洲航空得以認可，是因為一個低價航空公司擁有如此艷麗和迷人的空姐而聞名於世。有人說，航行中的美麗空姐比其提供的餐食更秀色可餐。"},{"pid":"1cbade32fcd2c0718e4bd4f38da17675c3c3cacf","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:15:34.000Z","msg":"6、Emirates 阿聯酋國際航空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n說到奢華程度，阿聯酋航空無疑是世界上最好的。它們在機上展示來自許多不同國度的美麗動人的空姐。她們燕瘦環肥，舉手投足卻不失高雅迷人。"},{"pid":"be9163dd0b1877f40562f33b7ae40c3cfc960d46","tid":1825242,"uid":136186,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:15:47.000Z","msg":"你正在進入內容農場"},{"pid":"915509368af74a7baf8107677b90bed21b0a48af","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"5、Cathay Pacific 香港國泰航空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乘坐過香港國泰航空公司的乘客大多會說它是亞洲最好的。穿着一身紅色的制服，國泰航空的空姐被譽為空中最美麗的僱員。"},{"pid":"e08b8782ee2ae652dae5ff3716296a7795dd7af4","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:16:24.000Z","msg":"4、Kingfisher Airlines 印度翠鳥航空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n翠鳥航空是印度首選的航空公司，道理是顯而易見的。通常，人們覺得他們摯愛翠鳥航空的原因是它擁有世界上最迷人的空姐。"},{"pid":"a8adbdf56ad689558280172d1f9ddb4093e5c9cd","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"3、Aeroflot Air 俄羅斯航空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是另外一個不錯的航空公司，空姐的制服也是紅色的。總體來說，這些俄國姑娘說不上特別時尚，然而，她們醒目的帽子和有型的領巾確實令人側目。"},{"pid":"8481d3bb3b0ab23185e5b52c3f8f6367a8b01bb3","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"2、Singapore Airlines 新加坡航空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你尋找的是最迷人，最友善的空中服務，那就非星加坡航空公司莫屬。它們的空姐穿着獨特的馬來風味的「沙龍卡巴雅裙」民族服飾，光彩迷人卻不失內斂。"},{"pid":"7b387fd7a56bff11f83ee6ce9e127bcc3410c16b","tid":1825242,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:18:16.000Z","msg":"1、Air France 法國航空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幸好，極其優雅的空姐彌補了法航提供的經濟艙位的不舒適。也許許多人都認為法國人樂觀和多情，但不要奢望這些美人的香吻，因為法國空姐對工作和娛樂是分得很清楚的。"},{"pid":"c748130560075437edb91ff2d7dbf597f0a4eec7","tid":1825242,"uid":315626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:18:26.000Z","ms